  "exploit_path": {
    "summary": "The attacker, operating from address 0x3f32c7cfb0a78ddea80a2384ceb4633099cbdc98, executed a price manipulation attack against P719Token on Binance Smart Chain. The primary attack transaction (0x9afcac8e82180fa5b2f346ca66cf6eb343cd1da5a2cd1b5117eb7eaaebe953b3) leveraged interactions with PancakeSwap Router (0x10ED43C718714eb63d5aA57B78B54704E256024E) and WBNB (0xbb4CdB9CBd36B01bD1cBaEBF2De08d9173bc095c). The attack pattern, classified as an 'inflate attack,' suggests the attacker manipulated token prices through liquidity pool interactions, likely exploiting a lack of proper price oracle protections or vulnerabilities in the token's swap mechanics. A proof-of-concept exploit was subsequently published by DeFiHackLabs, confirming the attack vector.",
    "steps": [
      {
        "title": "Step 1",
        "detail": "Attacker address 0x3f32c7cfb0a78ddea80a2384ceb4633099cbdc98 deploys an attack contract at 0x9afcac8e82180fa5b2f346ca66cf6eb343cd1da5 on BSC.",
        "evidence_refs": [
          "ev-004",
          "ev-012",
          "ev-031",
          "ev-035"
        ],
        "tx_hashes": []
      },
      {
        "title": "Step 2",
        "detail": "Attacker's contract performs price manipulation on the target token (P719Token at 0xfeb19ae8c0448f25de43a3afcb7b29c9cef6eff6) by executing swaps through PancakeSwap Router (0x10ED43C718714eb63d5aA57B78B54704E256024E) to inflate the token's price, likely interacting with a pool at 0x6beee2b57b064eac5f432fc19009e3e78734eabc.",
        "evidence_refs": [
          "ev-009",
          "ev-011",
          "ev-013",
          "ev-016"
        ],
